01:14:48,547 --> 01:14:50,914
-Let's leave.
-Oh, just relax.

763
01:14:51,094 --> 01:14:53,688
-Check, please!
-We haven't had desert yet.

764
01:14:54,000 --> 01:14:56,595
We'll get desert from room service.

765
01:15:00,221 --> 01:15:02,503
Keep 'm, boys.
The night is still young.

766
01:15:04,564 --> 01:15:06,410
Bye, honey.

767
01:15:21,096 --> 01:15:23,000
Oh, come on, I am used to this.

768
01:15:23,326 --> 01:15:25,225
Well, I am not.

769
01:15:30,704 --> 01:15:34,132
Listen, you are just visiting
the way I live.

770
01:15:34,899 --> 01:15:38,308
It would suit you fine to hide in that
hotel room till your train leaves.

771
01:15:38,574 --> 01:15:41,000
By all means, let's hide.

772
01:15:41,457 --> 01:15:44,921
You are so insistent on
everyone perceiving things the way you do.

773
01:15:44,999 --> 01:15:47,327
Oh yeah, I am making real
headway in that department.

774
01:15:47,421 --> 01:15:49,522
No fear, no confusion.
So self assured.

775
01:15:49,569 --> 01:15:51,362
I don't act that way to change the world,

776
01:15:51,386 --> 01:15:53,878
I act that way so the
goddamn world wont change me!

777
01:15:54,000 --> 01:15:57,000
-Lower your voice!
-Why? Is this a false issue?

778
01:15:58,818 --> 01:16:01,500
Is there some way to make
this easier?

779
01:16:02,614 --> 01:16:04,000
Yeah

780
01:16:05,550 --> 01:16:08,231
You take the car and I'll walk.

781
01:16:08,306 --> 01:16:10,204
And that is as easy as it gets.

782
01:16:16,130 --> 01:16:18,000
Does it have to unravel this quickly?

783
01:16:18,413 --> 01:16:20,019
Comes with the territory.

784
01:16:26,000 --> 01:16:29,259
-I'll walk!
-It's 12 miles, Vivian.

785
01:16:29,290 --> 01:16:32,000
Good!
Maybe it will wake me up!

