787
01:17:07,114 --> 01:17:09,369
# sends a letter, ..

788
01:17:10,376 --> 01:17:15,799
# of goodbye.

789
01:17:16,473 --> 01:17:19,006
# It's no secret, ..

790
01:17:19,762 --> 01:17:22,651
# you'll feel better, ..

791
01:17:23,299 --> 01:17:28,622
# if you cry.

792
01:17:29,817 --> 01:17:31,504
# When waking, from a bad dream ..

793
01:17:31,671 --> 01:17:33,741
Do you need me the way I need you?

794
01:17:34,550 --> 01:17:36,648
Yes. You know I do.

795
01:17:36,978 --> 01:17:37,978
# don't you ..

796
01:17:38,392 --> 01:17:41,642
# sometimes think it's real...

797
01:18:12,317 --> 01:18:13,309
Hi.

798
01:18:13,357 --> 01:18:16,362
Sorry to be late.
Walter couldn't find a tie.

799
01:18:19,260 --> 01:18:21,924
Oh, Silver, you are gorgeous.

800
01:18:27,798 --> 01:18:30,370
-Come on.
-How long will it last?

801
01:18:30,630 --> 01:18:31,977
5 minutes

802
01:18:41,978 --> 01:18:44,690
-I am glad to see you, Walter.
-I am glad to see you.

803
01:18:46,565 --> 01:18:48,729
-Thank you.
-My pleasure.

804
01:18:48,784 --> 01:18:50,502
Good morning to you all.

805
01:18:50,807 --> 01:18:52,226
Its Joe and Silvia.

806
01:18:52,522 --> 01:18:53,794
Silver!

807
01:18:54,296 --> 01:18:57,813
Well, Joe and Silver, no Silvia,
where are you, nice people, from?

808
01:18:57,982 --> 01:19:01,001
-Brooklyn.
-Charlottesville, Texas.

809
01:19:01,160 --> 01:19:03,628
That's where all the pretty girls are from.

810
01:19:03,840 --> 01:19:08,859
At this time I call upon gentleman
upstairs for a special blessing for you.

811
01:19:18,940 --> 01:19:20,917
-See me faint?
-I cried all the way through.

812
01:19:21,050 --> 01:19:23,350
It was real nice of you to come.

813
01:19:23,707 --> 01:19:25,257
Cay is the best.

814
01:19:30,766 --> 01:19:32,782
Don't say I've never
gave you anything.

815
01:19:36,580 --> 01:19:38,979
- Have a good trip.
-I see you in New York.

816
01:19:39,988 --> 01:19:41,086
Yes you will.

817
01:19:51,194 --> 01:19:54,000
Too bad things didn't
work out differently.

818
01:20:21,952 --> 01:20:24,733
Truth is that you don't
owe me one damn thing!

819
01:20:25,920 --> 01:20:28,608
Got nothing left, hang
on to you with, any more.

820
01:20:28,991 --> 01:20:31,000
I love you, Frances.

821
01:20:35,213 --> 01:20:37,422
I'll never accept what you do.

822
01:20:39,128 --> 01:20:40,430
I know.

823
01:20:43,893 --> 01:20:46,237
I just don't understand.

824
01:20:47,776 --> 01:20:49,500
Women together!

825
01:20:49,659 --> 01:20:52,051
She just reached in

826
01:20:52,500 --> 01:20:55,459
put a string of lights
around my heart.

827
01:20:58,102 --> 01:20:59,300
Don't keep her waiting.

828
01:20:59,462 --> 01:21:02,773
Oh, Frances, be happy for
somebody once in your life.

829
01:21:12,365 --> 01:21:13,680
Oh, God!

830
01:21:14,584 --> 01:21:18,359
Look at us! Standing in
the middle of the street.

831
01:21:20,211 --> 01:21:22,995
Next thing you know they
be talking about me.

832
01:21:36,605 --> 01:21:38,646
Is that it, then?

833
01:21:39,769 --> 01:21:42,310
I have know you longer
than anybody in my life.

834
01:21:44,468 --> 01:21:45,917
Meaning?

835
01:21:46,773 --> 01:21:48,853
That it will never "be it".

836
01:22:22,443 --> 01:22:24,931
Well, congratulations, Vivian.

837
01:22:25,536 --> 01:22:28,561
Like, you can head on back to
New York City a free woman.

838
01:22:28,884 --> 01:22:31,846
That is, of course, unless some
fellow here stole your heart.

839
01:22:33,095 --> 01:22:36,701
-How about a drink, to celebrate?
-I'd love one. But I have other plans.

840
01:22:36,762 --> 01:22:38,660
I think I understand.

841
01:22:39,505 --> 01:22:41,000
You look different.

842
01:22:41,913 --> 01:22:43,593
I see, you have yourself a new pin pal.

843
01:22:43,788 --> 01:22:46,382
No, I have much more
than that, Mr. Warner.

844
01:22:48,000 --> 01:22:49,289
Thank you.

845
01:22:51,036 --> 01:22:52,597
Good luck to you.

846
01:23:03,047 --> 01:23:04,944
Can I talk you into staying one more day?

847
01:23:05,062 --> 01:23:07,011
-Yes.
-Do you want me to?

848
01:23:07,461 --> 01:23:09,000
No.

849
01:23:10,822 --> 01:23:12,795
-I'll come back.
-When?

850
01:23:12,835 --> 01:23:14,000
Christmas.

851
01:23:14,594 --> 01:23:16,117
Christmas?

852
01:23:16,469 --> 01:23:19,000
-I don't know what you want.
-It's you I want.

853
01:23:34,556 --> 01:23:35,600
Cay?

854
01:23:36,464 --> 01:23:37,562
You are not coming?

855
01:23:38,387 --> 01:23:40,000
I'll see you at the station.

856
01:23:40,520 --> 01:23:42,000
Can we have dinner?

857
01:23:43,328 --> 01:23:44,523
No.

858
01:23:44,866 --> 01:23:45,984
Why?

859
01:23:47,594 --> 01:23:49,918
Because being with you is starting to hurt.

860
01:23:55,359 --> 01:23:56,826
I want...

861
01:24:00,000 --> 01:24:02,000
I want to say goodbye alone.

862
01:24:03,243 --> 01:24:05,640
We have been saying goodbye
from the beginning.

863
01:24:10,133 --> 01:24:11,548
I gotta go.

864
01:25:29,476 --> 01:25:33,020
-I put sugar...
-I won't stir.

865
01:25:36,646 --> 01:25:39,462
-I got another postcard from Silver today.
-How are they?

866
01:25:39,971 --> 01:25:41,769
Aren't all honeymoon cards
the same?

867
01:25:42,937 --> 01:25:46,601
"Incredible divine. Just like
a movie set. We'll never come back".

868
01:25:46,640 --> 01:25:49,429
-Come with me.
-Oh, sure thing.

869
01:25:51,021 --> 01:25:52,935
Can you just picture me with your set?

870
01:25:53,002 --> 01:25:55,898
If you want a sure thing, stay in Reno.

871
01:25:56,208 --> 01:25:59,806
As for my friends ... I managed to
get thru an hour with .. ahem ..

872
01:26:00,962 --> 01:26:02,413
Gwen.

873
01:26:04,048 --> 01:26:06,620
It's a nice offer, Vivian.

874
01:26:06,998 --> 01:26:09,326
but there are still...a few loose ends...

875
01:26:09,412 --> 01:26:10,741
-To say the least.

876
01:26:10,842 --> 01:26:12,733
-Then, why did you make it?

877
01:26:12,873 --> 01:26:14,770
Because I care about you.

878
01:26:14,897 --> 01:26:18,156
Because I think that you
deserve to live somewhere with...

879
01:26:18,621 --> 01:26:23,064
or near .. someone who sees how
wonderful you are ...

880
01:26:23,574 --> 01:26:26,971
exactly who you are.

881
01:26:27,280 --> 01:26:29,032
<font color="#ffff00">"All on board!"</font>

882
01:26:29,087 --> 01:26:32,000
That is why we'll never
finish this conversation.

883
01:26:37,294 --> 01:26:39,393
If it didn't please you, you
wouldn't have to stay.

884
01:26:42,402 --> 01:26:44,800
Yeah, we'll talk about it one of these days.

885
01:26:45,309 --> 01:26:47,507
Ride with me to the next station.

886
01:26:48,127 --> 01:26:51,515
-What can we settle in 40 minutes?
-I'll talk fast.

887
01:26:54,080 --> 01:26:56,500
Send me a postcard when you get there.

888
01:26:58,000 --> 01:27:02,000
-What is it that you want?
-Another 40 minutes with you.

